snippet.title: NUMOLITION - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
NUMOLITION will be available on the Nintendo eShop on the 16th of March! https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/numolition-switch/

Set up... add up... and BLOW UP!

An explosively addicting puzzle game starring Anique and her crew of demolition experts. With its unique, clever gameplay, cast of wacky characters and comic style, Numolition is a guaranteed blast for the whole family!

To stay up to date, visit the game's official website: https://www.numolition.com

#Numolition #nintendoswitch
